Anyways, forgiveness is something that was a hard concept for me to
grasp because of my past. Thank God, I have come to a better
understanding of it. Growing up, when wrong was done to me (by a
certain person), this person would keep saying they were sorry, day
after day after day. Yet, the same wrong was done to me. So they would
